        <li><a href="https://github.com/ShoKuno5" class="text-[#007aff] hover:underline">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://twitter.com/ReplicaSQ" class="text-[#007aff] hover:underline">X (Twitter)</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>